// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0192 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a33a8842-8b23-5676-9864-f2439737b93f

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
